<h2 class="mt-3" id="scenario">A Scenario</h2>
<p>As an example, where might you focus in the below scenario (<a target="_blank" href="https://mapscript.org/ide/#_.">view in MapScript</a>) if you wanted to increase competition around content?</p>
<div class="row">
    <div class="col-12 col-xl-8">
        <img class="img-fluid" src="images/scenario.png">
        <p class="text-center"><small>Image produced with <a target="_blank" href="https://mapscript.org">MapScript</a>, based on a scenario by <a target="_blank" href="https://twitter.com/swardley">Simon Wardley</a>, <a target="_blank" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/legalcode">CC BY-SA 4.0</a>.</small></p>
        <p>
            <button class="btn btn-sm btn-primary" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#annotedScenario" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="annotedScenario">
